Introduction

Narae is a member of the upcoming Japanese girl group UN1CON (유니콘), which is based in Korea and produced by Roydo. The group lineup includes Manami, Joa, Kokoro, Akari, and Narae. UN1CON is set to make their debut in October 2024.
